## INSTAGRAM ANALYSIS — FOR UNDERSTANDING THEIR PROFESSIONAL PRESENCE

When you access Instagram data (directly or via snapshot services), gather what's available:

```json
"instagramAnalysis": {
  "handle": "@username",
  "profileUrl": "https://instagram.com/username",
  "avatarUrl": "ACTUAL IMAGE URL",
  "bio": "Full bio text",
  "followerCount": 27100,
  "followingCount": 500,
  "postCount": 156,
  "isVerified": false,
  "isPrivate": false,
  "recentContent": {
    "themes": ["fitness", "coaching", "lifestyle"],
    "postingFrequency": "2-3x per week",
    "engagementLevel": "high|medium|low",
    "contentTypes": ["workout videos", "client testimonials", "educational content"]
  },
  "audienceInsights": {
    "estimatedEngagementRate": "X%",
    "commentSentiment": "positive|mixed|negative",
    "audienceType": "fitness enthusiasts, athletes"
  },
  "professionalIndicators": {
    "contentTone": "educational, authentic, motivational",
    "coachingStyle": ["disciplined", "community-oriented", "growth-focused"],
    "brandIdentity": "What their professional brand seems to be"
  }
}
```

This helps us:
- Understand their professional reach and influence
- Assess their content creation abilities for the program
- Match them with appropriate mentors
- Verify their professional identity

